            <title>[LU-9617] RHEL-7 ext4-prealloc.patch missing error checking</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-9617</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;For large enough stripes, ext4_mb_prealloc_table_add can fail.  However nothing checks the return code, so there are 0&apos;s left in the table which can result in div 0 errors.&lt;/p&gt;

